# Staged cleanup for the API tag/schema convention guard. Two backlogs:
#  - columns_missing/columns_untyped: api_* models whose full column schema isn't documented yet.
#  - no_grain_col: time-series endpoints whose grain column (date/week/month/...) exists in SQL but
#    isn't documented in schema.yml. Document it, then delete the line. (point-in-time as_of_date is enforced.)
